perator\" style=\"color:#A67F59;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);\">-</span>servers<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span>net<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span> com<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span> <span class=\"token number\" style=\"color:#990055;\">172800</span> IN  NS  l<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span>gtld<span class=\"token operator\" style=\"color:#A67F59;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);\">-</span>servers<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span>net<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span> com<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span> <span class=\"token number\" style=\"color:#990055;\">172800</span> IN  NS  m<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span>gtld<span class=\"token operator\" style=\"color:#A67F59;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);\">-</span>servers<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span>net<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span> </pre>\n	</blockquote>\n	<p style=\"margin-left:0.8em;font-size:1.6em;\">\n		也就是说，.com域名的解析结果，可以到这个13个服务器的任一台查询。细心的读者可能发现，这些服务器本身也是使用域名（比如a.gtld-servers.net.）标识，那么还得去查询它们指向的服务器，这样很容易造成循环查询。\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"margin-left:0.8em;font-size:1.6em;\">\n		因此，DNS 根区还会同时提供这些服务器的 IP 地址（IPv4 和 IPv6）。\n	</p>\n	<blockquote style=\"background-color:#F5F2F0;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, &quot;\">\n<pre class=\" language-bash\">a<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span>gtld<span class=\"token operator\" style=\"color:#A67F59;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);\">-</span>servers<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span>net<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#999999;\">.</span> <span class=\"token number\" style=\"color:#990055;\">172800</span> IN  A <span class=\"token number\" style=\"co